Job Details
We require property consultants working in all areas over Dubai but particularly focusing on the mainstream and prime markets. We welcome innovative individuals who can enhance our brand and look forward to a long term working relationship.Requirements:- minimum of 1 year UAE real estate experience- Proficient overall knowledge of Dubai- Excellent interpersonal and communication skills- Strong team player- Positive attitude- Driving license and own car- English speaking but other languages is an advantage.We offer:- Prime office location- Marketing and administrative support- Hands-on experienced management- Paper and online advertising- CRM Software for Advertising and management- Team culture- Enjoyable working environmentPlease send your CV to us if you have the necessary qualifications! only qualified applicant will be contacted once shortlisted.
